KNOWN DEPENDANCIES
------------------
prngd or egd should be available to provide entropy.

ERRORS/MISCELLANEOUS
--------------------

Shared libraries have been built with an extra minor number corresponding
to the subrelease (ie d=4).
I deemed this necessary since binary compatibility between releases is not
guaranteed by openssl developers.
This means that 0.9.7c may not necessarily be binary compatible with 0.9.7d.

Please see the INSTALL document for further information on this issue.
